Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:38.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:40.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At least we're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:44.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're better off wielding\nhoes than swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:48.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought we'd all be dead,\nbut we can go back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:51.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to that\npriestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:53.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:57.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, he's conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:01:59.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brace up, Yohei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:02.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The priestess's medicine worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:05.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess!\NYohei is revived!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:21.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Evil still seeks this man's life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:27.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:30.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing. He'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:32.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He can probably get up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:37.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does a priestess named Kikyo\nserve this temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:46.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you the one who tends\nto soldiers injured in war...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:48.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,regardless of which side\nthey fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:50.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and who uses strange powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:53.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to bring back even those near death\nback to life?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:55.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No strange powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:58.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only knowledge of healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:01.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can tell us at the castle.\NCome with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:11.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Kagewaki, master of\nthe Hitomi Clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,has been in delicate health\nsince birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He recently became the head\nof the clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,after his father passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:21.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His condition has\nsteadily weakened...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:25.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and yet, he won't let physicians\nnear him, not even his own vassals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No one may pass!\NThe order is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:33.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have brought a priestess\nwho will cure Lord Kagewaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:35.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, the lord forbid\nentry to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:37.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The lord refuses to see anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:41.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this castle?\NThis shroud of evil?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:47.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this man is the lord?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sense no life in him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As if he is dead from\nneck down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:10.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:14.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But she refuses to stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:19.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She claimed to cure your illness\nand forced herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:20.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:22.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:23.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:27.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You there... what is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo is alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:38.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The woman I myself set up\nfifty years ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:42.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the woman who died,\ntaking the Sacred Jewel with her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:43.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}is still alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This woman... What's going{\i0} on... {\i1}?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?\NThis is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These, too.\NAll withered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:01.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NThere's no dry spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:03.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suddenly this past month...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:10.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-it's red... like blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:11.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:23.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... So it rained\npieces of demon carcasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:27.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... it was so creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Our fields are ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:32.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not only our fields...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:35.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the elderly, the young\nand the weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:37.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so many of them\nhave succumbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:39.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I expect that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:43.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There must be a source for\na very strong miasma near by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So we're gonna help again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do we really have time\nfor this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:55.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to find Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:58.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you apologize,\NI won't forgive you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:02.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}About Naraku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:04.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That arrow that Kagome shot...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:07.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}should have caused a\n{\i1}very deep wound.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:11.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As strong as he may be, Naraku would\nbe out of commission for a while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:18.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:22.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've already received a gratuity.\NWe must help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:23.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When'd you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:26.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't take it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:29.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And don't you get gratuities\n{\i1}after{\i0} you do something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After the fact,\nthey usually give less.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You amaze me!\NYou dirty priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:36.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:43.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure the miasma source is\nover at the base of that mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was wondering if there is\na demon other than Naraku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:49.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who could create a miasma\nso strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:52.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Other than Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:56.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:00.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you make of\nthe Lord's illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:03.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... I think it may be\nbeyond my skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:07.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see... I knew it was no\nordinary illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So even you will\nabandon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:15.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am merely a priestess.\NPlease permit me to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:22.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me, but the Lord has\nforbidden you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We will have you stay here for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo is supposed to\nhave died...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can wait to kill her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:38.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}until after I discover\nher true self.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:41.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonight, my wishes\nwill be fulfilled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:44.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've found an interesting woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:53.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because of the miasma, not even\na blade of grass grows here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:55.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll soon be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:58.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on in\nthis mountain anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:06.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:08.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The miasma comes from...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:11.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:17.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're still not fully recovered.\NYou must take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:19.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango and Kagome,\nyou wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:21.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's only a demon-slaying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:24.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,no sense in all of us\ngoing in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, the miasma doesn't seem\nto bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:30.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:37.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be careful. This miasma\nis pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:43.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can feel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:45.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}a strong whirling miasma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:47.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shall I go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:04.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And bring me a bow\nand arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:08.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:10.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The miasma is getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:13.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... Kagome, how can\nyou put up with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:15.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh... for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:23.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this? Something's\npulling me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:25.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on inside the cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:29.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if Inuyasha and\NMaster Miroku are okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The miasma is getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:39.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you doing, Miroku?!\NSo hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:43.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have undergone training,\nso I have some endurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An average human\nwould not stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:56.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's something...\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:10.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon remains?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:37.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demons fighting each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:53.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hundreds of demons have been\nfighting and killing each other here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:56.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those who lost and their debris\nshowered the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These are the remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:01.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awful. But why are they doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:22.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The last demon standing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Merged its body with the other's!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:31.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why can't I get out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:38.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The last demon standing was\nsupposed to leave here alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:41.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be that this{\i0} is... {\i1}?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:46.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is there another demon here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:48.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:49.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lemme go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:54.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If my hunch is correct...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:57.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! This is bad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:01.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:07.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're taking too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:08.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:13.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not you, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:15.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you go in there in\nyour condition, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:18.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, let's get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:20.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's bad for your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:33.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:37.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is Inuyasha inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:47.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:49.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That priestess is Kikyo,\nisn't she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:51.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you following her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! Shippo, you stay\nwith Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:58.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know why she's here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,something evil is\ngoing on inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take Kirara with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:07.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be careful, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:08.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you! Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:19.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The souls of the dead inside my body\nare trying to get out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are they drawn by the\nmiasma in this cave?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can feel something\nother than the miasma...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:30.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it from the man in\nthe castle... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:37.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next, the finishing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:47.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The wound is closing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:50.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold back your sword, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:51.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do {\i1}not{\i0} fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:55.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! If I don't fight,\NI'll get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:56.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is just like the {\i1}Fuko{\i0} spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The same method to create {\i1}Kodoku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:02.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fuko{\i0} spell?\N{\i1}Kodoku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:04.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With the {\i1}Fuko{\i0} spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:09.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,poisonous worms and lizards\nare placed in one pot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,have them kill each\nother off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:14.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The last one remaining alive then\nbecomes a creature called {\i1}Kodoku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:21.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can say that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:24.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:27.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will be the only one to live\nand get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no choice, do I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:40.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is turning out bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unless the spell cast in here\nis broken...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:46.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inu...yasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:14:59.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:06.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The souls of the dead\nare leaving{\i0} me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:12.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This miasma is from Kodoku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:23.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:25.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo is here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:49.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soon it will come out...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:53.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}With my spell, I sealed\ncountless demons in there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}One by one, they killed each other...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:59.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}until only one remains victorious...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that one will become...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:05.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}my new body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:08.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:16.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:38.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What... ?!\NI sense the Sacred Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:42.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not this fragment...\NThere's another.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:45.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone else with\na Sacred Jewel fragment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:46.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It couldn't be...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The miasma is absorbing\NKikyo's souls of the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:55.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and getting thicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right?\NHang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:02.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku... what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:12.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This cave is under\na {\i1}Fuko{\i0} spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:13.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unless we stop Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:16.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he will become fused\nwith the demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:17.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fused?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:20.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sense the presence\nof the Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:21.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this a trap then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:24.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The strength of this miasma...\NThere's no mistaking it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This woman is not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:34.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will devour her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not touch Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay cool, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:54.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get real, will ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:56.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will protect Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will protect Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:07.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!\NWhat're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:21.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to pull Kikyo up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:26.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otherwise, Inuyasha will continue\nfighting for Kikyo's sake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:30.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha would never stand by\nand watch Kikyo's slaughter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:32.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a bit jealous, though...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you conscious?\NCan you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:41.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So foolish...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:46.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By your coming here,\NInuyasha will lose you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:52.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:56.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is trying so hard\nto save you! Yet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:04.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:08.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:10.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:26.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:32.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:34.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The spell is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:36.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The miasma is disintegrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:49.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:50.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:53.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:56.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... but Kikyo was!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:02.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:06.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:39.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since you destroyed\nhis body, Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku needed to create\na new body for himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why he used the {\i1}Fuko{\i0} spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:45.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So the mountain miasma lured you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:49.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and you entered the cave\nupon which I had cast my spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:55.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you could have fused into\nthis body, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:00.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this the woman who\nbroke the spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:05.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks to her, I'm able to\npossess a new body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:08.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The spell was broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:11.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so that Kikyo could\nsave Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:16.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It looks like this woman\nis Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:19.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the one who followed you\nin death fifty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:22.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not touch Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:26.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,with your filthy hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:37.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:41.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn...damn it all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:49.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't understand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:53.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it's true that Kikyo wanted\nto save Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:55.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}instead of breaking the spell...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:59.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}why didn't she aim the arrow\nat the demon Kodoku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:03.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Instead, Kikyo broke the spell...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:07.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and enabled me to\npossess a new body...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.79,0:23:49.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku now possesses\na new body.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.46,0:23:53.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His renewed power seizes upon\nthe dark side of our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.76,0:23:56.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's feelings for Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:23:58.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku's weakness,\nhis Wind Tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:01.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, still troubled by\NKohaku's phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.64,0:24:03.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo, are you going to save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.90,0:24:06.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those are the Sacred Jewel fragments\nthat we've gathered!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.91,0:24:08.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you going to\ndo with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.44,0:24:12.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Kikyo, Captured by Naraku!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.01,0:24:13.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
